description:
Here is a gold mine of knowledge and wisdom passed on by one of the greatest jazz pianists to ever grace the planet. Mulgrew Miller shares some words from a mentor to a student during his interview with Jazz Bassist Jonah Jonathan in February 2012. Mulgrew Miller passed away far to soon at only 57 years old from complications from a massive stroke. R.I.P Mulgrew Miller August 13th, 1955 - May 29th 2013.

Thanks for watching and please subscribe to us and give a like button. Subscribing really helps us out because you are notified when new videos come out. Share this video on social media if you enjoy it because it helps keep jazz alive. Thank you! 

Visit Our Website:

https://jazzmusiciansvoice.net/

#MulgrewMiller #Jazz #Piano #Memorial
title: Remembering Mulgrew Miller: Beautiful Words Of Wisdom
fulltitle: Remembering Mulgrew Miller: Beautiful Words Of Wisdom
